{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f42fd212c3","title":"给高×的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"12ad0a1597","index":0,"year":1964,"month":3,"day":18,"articleId":"f42fd212c3"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"156848dba1","type":"paragraph","text":"谈到人民日报上“桌子的哲学”的讨论，主席说：观念是从实践来的。人们从土堆，石堆，或者别的东西中，逐渐有了桌子的想法。做桌子，把想法提高了一步，是一个飞跃。而做出来的桌子同原来想法已经不同，又进了一步，这又是一个飞跃。王若水同志可以写篇东西来补正一下。C","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"4ac79c680f","type":"paragraph","text":"×××谈到这个讨论时说：如象有的文章说的，人造的东西都是先有观念，这不对，这就成了唯心主义了。","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"1cf0314d40","type":"paragraph","text":"××说，报低要把两方面的意见都登出来。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"f69536fc92","type":"paragraph","text":"（据×××说：报纸理论版近来登了些讨论，但主席还没有形成已经有改进的印象。因此康生同志提出，决定在学术版挂起“学术研究”的牌子，并准备一周出两次。）","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"cf61515093","type":"paragraph","text":"对新华社的指示","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"e2792085db","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年春）你们新华社只有几千人，太少了，恐怕是世界通迅社中最小的吧！可以办得更大一些。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"7bec4afa32","type":"paragraph","text":"给华罗庚的信","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"c4e67f313b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年三月十八日）华罗庚先生","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"d3e2ba7b1d","type":"paragraph","text":"诗和信己经收读，壮志凌云，可喜可贺。肃此。敬颂教旗","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"fefd13f807","type":"paragraph","text":"毛溪东","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"71096277b4","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年三月十八日给高的信","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"1ae5bfd725","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年三月十八日）高×先生：","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"6d117b3849","type":"paragraph","text":"寄书寄词，还有二信，均已收到，极为威谢，高文两册，我很爱读，肃此，敬颂吉安。","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"18132feff1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛东","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"},{"id":"7881bfca17","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年三月十八日98","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3"}],"page":{"id":"c9c19b41a5","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"f42fd212c3","start":111,"end":111}}}},"__N_SSG":true}